Version 20.1.1.2
=============

- Hotfixes for More Unhandled Crashes (this should be the last of the major ones)
- Fixed Crashes related to the Updater
- Fixed Forced Auto Boot Mode Not Perserving or Applying Settings Before or After Game Launch

Please Inform Me if you still have issues with the program so I can figure out what the problem is if it still exists:

- Being Unable to Run this Program without ADMIN Privliages
- Unexplained Crashes related to Downloading Updates/Mods
